title: Spacious new!! 4 bed 2 bath apartment
posting_body: ['Spacious new!!', '4 bed 2 bath apartment next door to Summer Village Apartments.', 'This popular floor plan is now available for as low as $960.00 a month.', 'Give us a call or stop by our office at 808 W. 2nd', 'Ave Acacia Apts.', 'to check out all of the amenities.', '24-Hour Emergency Maintenance Apply, Lease, Work Orders, Pay Rent, and many other On-line easy to use features Weekly Landscaping Maintenance Close to Walking/Biking Trails Walk to Chico State!', 'No need parking pass!', 'Next to Restaurants, Grocery Stores, Downtown Shopping, and Transportation./.Washer/Dryer in units and all new upgraded modern kitchens ,granite countertops with all new stainless steel appliances including dishwashers.', 'Bathrooms redone beautifully and hardwood floor throughout..', 'If you are interested please send call;', 'show contact info']
